      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved specimen, offered in true showroom condition. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, featuring flawless coachwork and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that mirrors its initial delivery. For the sophisticated buyer seeking a vehicle devoid of compromise, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class.",
